vlc-discordrpc-plugin (1.1.0) stable; urgency=medium

  * Release version 1.1.0.
  * The plugin now displays the playlist (by default, it is disabled).
  * The presence type has also been changed to Playing, Listening, and Watching, depending on the type of multimedia content.

