vlc-discordrpc-plugin (1.0.0) stable; urgency=medium

  * Release version 1.0.0.
  * Provides integration between VLC Media Player and Discord.
  * Built with CMake, installs plugin into /usr/lib/x86_64-linux-gnu/vlc/plugins/misc/.

 -- Zukaritasu <zukaritasu@gmail.com>  Mon, 17 Feb 2026 21:19:00 -0400

